---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="SAP Roll-Out & Lokalizasyon">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="relative pt-40 pb-24 bg-surface-container overflow-hidden">
        <div class="max-w-[1920px] mx-auto px-12 md:px-24">
            <div class="text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary font-bold text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">SAP ROLL-OUT & LOKALİZASYON</span>
                <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold font-headline text-on-background tracking-tight mb-8">Sınır Ötesi SAP Operasyonları ve Lokalizasyon</h1>
                <p class="text-xl text-on-surface-variant font-body leading-relaxed">Global SAP mimarinizi yeni pazarlara uyarlarken, yerel mevzuat risklerini sıfırlayın ve operasyonel bütünlüğü koruyun.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- What is Roll-Out -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-surface">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-8">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold font-headline mb-6">SAP Roll-Out Nedir?</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed mb-6">SAP Roll-Out, mevcut bir SAP sisteminin sıfırdan kurulması değil; halihazırda çalışan bir yapının yeni ülkelere, şirketlere veya operasyonlara genişletilmesidir.</p>
            <p class="text-lg text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Bu süreçte temel referans, daha önce oluşturulmuş <strong class="text-on-background">global SAP şablonudur (global template)</strong>. Amaç, tüm organizasyonu tek bir standart altında toplarken yerel gereksinimleri de eksiksiz şekilde karşılamaktır.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Standardization & Flexibility -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-on-background text-white">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold font-headline mb-6">Standartlaşma ve Esneklik Dengesi</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">Roll-Out projelerinde en kritik nokta, global standardı korurken yerel ihtiyaçlara uyum sağlamaktır. Bu yaklaşım, hem kontrolü hem de sürdürülebilirliği garanti eder.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-5 rounded-xl flex items-start gap-4 hover:border-primary-container/50 transition-all">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-container text-xl mt-0.5">verified</span>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">Mevcut SAP tasarımına bağlı kalınarak ilerlenir</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-5 rounded-xl flex items-start gap-4 hover:border-primary-container/50 transition-all">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-container text-xl mt-0.5">compare</span>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">Fit/Gap analizleri ile farklar belirlenir</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-5 rounded-xl flex items-start gap-4 hover:border-primary-container/50 transition-all">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-container text-xl mt-0.5">tune</span>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">Yerel gereksinimler kontrollü şekilde entegre edilir</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-5 rounded-xl flex items-start gap-4 hover:border-primary-container/50 transition-all">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-container text-xl mt-0.5">shield</span>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">Global yapı bozulmadan genişleme sağlanır</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Turkey & Global Localization -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-surface-container-lowest">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
                <div>
                    <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary font-bold text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">LOKALİZASYON</span>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold font-headline mb-6">Türkiye ve Global Lokalizasyon</h2>
                    <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed mb-4">Farklı ülkelere açılan şirketler için lokalizasyon, projenin en kritik parçalarından biridir. Özellikle Türkiye gibi dinamik regülasyonlara sahip pazarlarda tüm gereksinimler tek bir yapı altında ele alınır.</p>
                    <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed text-sm">Global template korunurken, tüm bu gereksinimler SAP üzerinde standart, denetlenebilir ve sürdürülebilir bir modele dönüştürülür.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-6 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/20 hover:border-primary/50 transition-all">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl mb-3">gavel</span>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-sm mb-1">Vergi & Muhasebe</h4>
                        <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-xs">Yerel vergi ve muhasebe mevzuatına tam uyum</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-6 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/20 hover:border-primary/50 transition-all">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl mb-3">receipt_long</span>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-sm mb-1">e-Dönüşüm</h4>
                        <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-xs">e-Fatura, e-Arşiv, e-İrsaliye, e-Defter</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-6 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/20 hover:border-primary/50 transition-all">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl mb-3">assessment</span>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-sm mb-1">Raporlama</h4>
                        <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-xs">Yerel raporlama ve beyan yükümlülükleri</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-6 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/20 hover:border-primary/50 transition-all">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl mb-3">hub</span>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-sm mb-1">GİB Entegrasyonları</h4>
                        <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-xs">GİB uyumlu entegrasyonlar</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Inbound / Outbound -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-surface">
        <div class="max-w-[1920px] mx-auto px-12 md:px-24">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
                <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-12 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-outline-variant/20 hover:border-primary/50 transition-all group">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-all">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl text-primary group-hover:text-white">flight_land</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold font-headline mb-4">Türkiye'ye Gelen Şirketler</h3>
                    <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Global SAP sistemlerinin Türkiye operasyonları için mevzuata tam uyumlu lokalizasyonu ve rollout projeleri. Merkezi mimariyi koruyarak yerel zorunlulukları karşılıyoruz.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-12 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-outline-variant/20 hover:border-primary/50 transition-all group">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-all">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl text-primary group-hover:text-white">flight_takeoff</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold font-headline mb-4">Yurtdışına Açılan Şirketler</h3>
                    <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Türk şirketlerinin küresel operasyonları için merkez SAP yapısının uluslararası standartlara (IFRS) ve yabancı ülke mevzuatlarına uyarlanması.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Typical Use Cases -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-primary text-white">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8">
            <div class="text-center mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold font-headline mb-4">Tipik Kullanım Senaryoları</h2>
                <p class="text-white/60">Roll-Out projeleri genellikle şu durumlarda devreye alınır:</p>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                <div class="bg-white/10 border border-white/20 p-6 rounded-xl flex items-start gap-4">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl mt-0.5">public</span>
                    <p class="text-sm">Yeni bir ülkeye açılım</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white/10 border border-white/20 p-6 rounded-xl flex items-start gap-4">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl mt-0.5">corporate_fare</span>
                    <p class="text-sm">Grup şirketlerinin merkezi SAP yapısına dahil edilmesi</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white/10 border border-white/20 p-6 rounded-xl flex items-start gap-4">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl mt-0.5">factory</span>
                    <p class="text-sm">Yeni fabrika, depo veya lojistik merkezlerinin entegrasyonu</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white/10 border border-white/20 p-6 rounded-xl flex items-start gap-4">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl mt-0.5">merge</span>
                    <p class="text-sm">Satın alınan şirketlerin mevcut sisteme uyarlanması</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white/10 border border-white/20 p-6 rounded-xl flex items-start gap-4">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl mt-0.5">upgrade</span>
                    <p class="text-sm">Mevcut yapının kademeli olarak yeni SAP versiyonlarına taşınması</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white/10 border border-white/20 p-6 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
                    <p class="text-center font-bold text-sm">Tek sistem, tek veri modeli,<br/>merkezi kontrol.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- End-to-End Methodology -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-surface-container-lowest">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8">
            <div class="text-center mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold font-headline mb-4">Uçtan Uca Roll-Out Metodolojisi</h2>
                <p class="text-on-surface-variant">Yapılandırılmış ve kontrollü bir süreç, öngörülebilir ve başarılı sonuçlar sağlar.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-7 gap-4">
                <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-6 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/20 text-center hover:border-primary/50 transition-all">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 text-sm font-bold">1</div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-xs">Template Tasarımı</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-6 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/20 text-center hover:border-primary/50 transition-all">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 text-sm font-bold">2</div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-xs">Lokal Uyarlama</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-6 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/20 text-center hover:border-primary/50 transition-all">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 text-sm font-bold">3</div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-xs">Entegrasyon & Veri</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-6 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/20 text-center hover:border-primary/50 transition-all">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 text-sm font-bold">4</div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-xs">Fit/Gap Workshop</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-6 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/20 text-center hover:border-primary/50 transition-all">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 text-sm font-bold">5</div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-xs">Test & QA</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-6 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/20 text-center hover:border-primary/50 transition-all">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 text-sm font-bold">6</div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-xs">Cutover</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-6 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/20 text-center hover:border-primary/50 transition-all">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 text-sm font-bold">7</div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-xs">Hypercare</h4>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Key Benefits -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-surface">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8">
            <div class="text-center mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold font-headline mb-4">Sağladığı Temel Faydalar</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/20 hover:shadow-lg transition-all flex items-start gap-4">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-2xl mt-0.5 shrink-0">public</span>
                    <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm">Çok ülkeli yapıda standartlaşma ve merkezi yönetim</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/20 hover:shadow-lg transition-all flex items-start gap-4">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-2xl mt-0.5 shrink-0">gavel</span>
                    <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm">Yerel mevzuatlara tam uyum</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/20 hover:shadow-lg transition-all flex items-start gap-4">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-2xl mt-0.5 shrink-0">savings</span>
                    <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm">Entegrasyon ve geliştirme maliyetlerinde düşüş</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/20 hover:shadow-lg transition-all flex items-start gap-4">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-2xl mt-0.5 shrink-0">visibility</span>
                    <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm">Global raporlama ve finansal görünürlük artışı</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/20 hover:shadow-lg transition-all flex items-start gap-4">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-2xl mt-0.5 shrink-0">share</span>
                    <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm">Süreç iyileştirmelerinin tüm organizasyona yayılması</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/20 hover:shadow-lg transition-all flex items-start gap-4">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-2xl mt-0.5 shrink-0">trending_up</span>
                    <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm">SAP yatırımının hızlı ve verimli şekilde ölçeklenmesi</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="py-20">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-8">
            <div class="bg-on-background rounded-md p-12 text-center relative overflow-hidden">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold font-headline text-white mb-6">Sınır Ötesi Dönüşüm Stratejinizi Planlayalım</h2>
                <p class="text-slate-400 mb-8">Global SAP mimarinizi yeni pazarlara uyarlarken, yerel mevzuat risklerini uzman ekibimizle analiz edin.</p>
                <div class="flex justify-center">
                    <a href="/iletisim" class="bg-primary text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-md font-bold hover:bg-primary-container transition-colors shadow-lg">Değerlendirme Başlatın</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
